title: Expert Java Engineer and Programming Mentor
description: Nathan Snow is a highly skilled software engineer specialising in Java and has experience in Spring Boot, JavaScript, MySQL, PostgreSQL, REST APIs, and DevOps. As an Aussie software engineer, he brings a unique perspective and deep understanding of the latest technologies. He is also an experienced programming mentor with a talent for sharing his knowledge and helping others to excel. I highly recommend Nathan for any Java development or DevOps-related roles, and I am confident that his skills and mentorship will make him an asset to any team.
